  "description": "If you own real estate in California, you need to have an attorney prepare a will and trust for you.   The following are answers to some basic questions we often receive from our clients. What is a Will and Trust A will and trust are legal documents that provide a written declaration as to how you want your assets distributed after you pass away.  We always prepare trusts for our clients as they can provide tax advantages and can be utilized as a tool to avoid death taxes and inheritance taxes later.  When you prepare a trust, you appoint a..."
